  <diagram id="AYvzZGNO3fj8dr65Hd_c" name="Análise &amp; QD">
    <mxGraphModel dx="934" dy="619" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="oufH4ouA1xHbebBQO13V-1" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-ecd7a3f1-7fff-1673-5ed6-69fb6531e1b2&quot; style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Consolidação e validação:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Reunir os dados brutos de todas as fazendas parceiras (por ex., leituras de balanças, sensores de ordenha) e aplicar filtros de qualidade, identificando anomalias ou erros de entrada (ex.: valores impossíveis ou sensores desconectados).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Garantia de integridade:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-wrap-mode: wrap; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; Verificar calibração de equipamentos e confiabilidade das medições, acionando equipes de campo ou fornecedores de IoT se necessário para corrigir problemas. Isso assegura que decisões posteriores sejam baseadas em dados corretos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Análise operacional inicial:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-wrap-mode: wrap; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; Gerar relatórios operacionais básicos e &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;painéis de controle&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-wrap-mode: wrap; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; para cada fazenda, resumindo indicadores de desempenho (ganho de peso diário, produção por vaca, etc.). Esses insights iniciais servem tanto para uso interno quanto para feedback rápido aos parceiros.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-size: 11pt; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Comunicação de dados:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; text-wrap-mode: wrap; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-size: 11pt; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt; Manter diálogo com a equipe de Parcerias Rurais, informando sobre quaisquer irregularidades nos dados ou tendências observadas, para que o cliente (fazenda) seja notificado e participe da solução (por exemplo, um sensor de leite travado que precisa de manutenção).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="400" width="560" x="110" y="110" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
