  <diagram id="N_Ehll5D5dB3q8tC8Sxr" name="Operações de  Campo">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1152" dy="622" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="Kc-XlXgHNHJbHHAXmhwf-1" value="&lt;b style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: nowrap; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Coordenação de Operações de Campo&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="240" y="60" width="380" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="Kc-XlXgHNHJbHHAXmhwf-2" value="&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-752cd776-7fff-c56a-ebe4-3338518dfabc&quot; style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Orientação e treinamento remoto:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Comunicar às equipes da fazenda (capatazes, tratadores, ordenhadores) as &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;mudanças de manejo recomendadas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; e esclarecer o “porquê” de cada uma. Por exemplo, se o modelo indicar que vacas de primeira lactação precisam de suplementação X, a coordenação de campo garante que a equipe entenda como e quando fornecer essa suplementação. Pode envolver produção de manuais simples, checklists ou até breves treinamentos via vídeo chamadas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Acompanhamento da execução:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Verificar se as ações acordadas foram implementadas no dia a dia. Isso pode incluir monitorar remotamente indicadores (ex.: se a curva de peso reagiu à mudança alimentar conforme esperado) ou solicitar feedback fotográfico/informações qualitativas da fazenda. Em casos críticos, o coordenador de operações pode &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;agendar visitas in loco&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; para ver de perto a situação e auxiliar no ajuste fino das práticas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Feedback para a área de dados:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Trazer informações do campo que os dados por si só não explicam. Por exemplo: se um determinado lote não ganhou peso apesar de a recomendação ter sido seguida, o que pode ter ocorrido? Talvez uma doença não detectada ou qualidade do alimento diferente. Esse retorno qualitativo da realidade é essencial para aprimorar os modelos e evitar conclusões incorretas. A equipe de campo age, assim, como &quot;sensores humanos&quot; complementando os sensores IoT.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Logística e suporte operacional:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Auxiliar as fazendas na adoção de novas tecnologias (instalação de um novo sensor, por exemplo) ou na reorganização de alguma rotina. Embora não sejam “mão na massa” permanente, os coordenadores podem conectar a fazenda a prestadores de serviço, fornecedores de insumos ou profissionais (nutricionistas, veterinários) conforme necessidade identificada pelos dados. Em suma, catalisam a &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;mudança operacional&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; de forma suave, para que o produtor veja valor e não sinta que é “mais trabalho” sem propósito.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="110" y="90" width="560" height="630" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dPjL-KtNVsM-NbV1DidE-1" value="Zootecnista" style="shape=umlActor;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;html=1;outlineConnect=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="190" y="830" width="20" height="38" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dPjL-KtNVsM-NbV1DidE-2" value="Cientista de Dados" style="shape=umlActor;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;html=1;outlineConnect=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="320" y="830" width="20" height="38" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1pi5i-AhnfT4kunzE91Z-1" value="" style="image;sketch=0;aspect=fixed;html=1;points=[];align=center;fontSize=12;image=img/lib/mscae/Azure_Home.svg;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="190" y="748" width="50" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="1pi5i-AhnfT4kunzE91Z-2" value="Implementação" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="160" y="788" width="110" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram id="BYGCVUxowwtUW41fs4K6" name="Finanças &amp; Estratégia">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1152" dy="622" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="o-fhaxCWsX2_4znks3SH-1" value="&lt;b style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: nowrap; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Finanças e Estratégia&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="280" y="70" width="200" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="o-fhaxCWsX2_4znks3SH-3" value="&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-a4367c7b-7fff-6afc-624d-5ec5544530f0&quot; style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Modelagem de receita e acompanhamento de KPIs:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Desenvolver e atualizar o modelo financeiro baseado nas parcerias. Isso inclui calcular periodicamente os lucros incrementais gerados em cada fazenda devido às melhorias implementadas e a parcela de participação da startup em cada caso. A transparência e precisão nesses cálculos fortalecem a confiança dos parceiros. Além disso, monitorar indicadores-chave como &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;ROI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; para os clientes, margem da startup, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;payback&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; de cada projeto, etc., informando decisões estratégicas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Captação de recursos e investimento:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Formular planos de negócio e apresentações (pitch decks) para investidores, se for o caso de levantar capital para expandir. A área estratégica deve comunicar como a estrutura organizacional enxuta e tecnológica da empresa permite escalar ganhos rapidamente conforme mais fazendas aderem. Também avalia opções de financiamento de equipamentos IoT, parcerias com instituições (ex.: programas governamentais de inovação no agro) para alavancar crescimento.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Planejamento estratégico e expansão:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Traçar cenários de crescimento futuro – por exemplo, expandir o modelo para outras regiões ou países, ou adicionar novos &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;produtos/serviços&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; (p. ex.: gestão de culturas agrícolas em rotação com pecuária, ou marketplace para compra coletiva de insumos pelas fazendas parceiras). A equipe define prioridades e garante que a estrutura organizacional possa absorver essas expansões. Isso inclui planejar contratações conforme marcos de crescimento (evitando inchar a equipe cedo demais) – dado que em startups a prioridade inicial é flexibilidade, e a formalização vem conforme a carga de trabalho exige.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Governança e processos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Estabelecer &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;guidelines&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; para tomada de decisão, aprovação de despesas, políticas de repartição de resultados, etc. Em suma, trazer maturidade gerencial conforme a empresa cresce, sem engessar a inovação. Por exemplo, implementar OKRs (Objectives and Key Results) para alinhar as diferentes equipes em torno das metas estratégicas trimestrais/anuais.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="80" y="100" width="560" height="650" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dwSexMY9MbDyDLr5FaRC-1" value="CEO" style="shape=umlActor;verticalLabelPosition=bottom;verticalAlign=top;html=1;outlineConnect=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="160" y="860" width="20" height="40" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dwSexMY9MbDyDLr5FaRC-2" value="" style="image;sketch=0;aspect=fixed;html=1;points=[];align=center;fontSize=12;image=img/lib/mscae/Chart.svg;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="145" y="750" width="50" height="48" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="dwSexMY9MbDyDLr5FaRC-4" value="Estrategia" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="130" y="798" width="80" height="30" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
  </diagram>
  <diagram id="Iod6E8VItrJrVZDZetmi" name="Squads">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1152" dy="622" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="850" pageHeight="1100" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <mxCell id="2GdyIjArwxJhsU-BfKCi-1" value="&lt;b style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: nowrap; background-color: rgb(236, 236, 236); text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Squads&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="410" y="90" width="100" height="50" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="2GdyIjArwxJhsU-BfKCi-2" value="&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-8b1d20fe-7fff-f275-f90f-ef3321a21d5f&quot; style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding-inline-start: 48px;&quot;&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Maior foco no cliente e produto:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Cada squad age quase como uma mini-startup voltada a gerar valor para um cliente ou desafio específico. Isso aumenta a proximidade com as necessidades reais da fazenda e permite pivots rápidos se algo não funciona, sem impactar toda a organização.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Comunicação e rapidez:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Em vez de passar por várias camadas hierárquicas, a comunicação dentro de um squad é direta entre especialistas. Um problema nos dados da Fazenda Alfa, por exemplo, pode ser resolvido em conjunto pelo engenheiro e pelo cientista de dados imediatamente, sem “jogar para outro setor”. A &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;comunicação aberta&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; e frequente entre diferentes funções torna a resolução de problemas mais ágil.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Inovação contínua:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Times pequenos e autônomos tendem a experimentar mais e sentir-se donos do processo. Cada squad pode adotar a metodologia ágil que preferir (Scrum, Kanban etc.) para gerir suas tarefas, contanto que entreguem resultados alinhados à estratégia geral. Essa liberdade controlada estimula a criatividade e a responsabilidade.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Escalabilidade modular:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Novas fazendas ou produtos podem ser atendidos formando novos squads, sem necessariamente recriar toda a estrutura organizacional. Por exemplo, ao fechar parceria com 5 fazendas novas, a empresa pode criar um &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Tribo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; (conjunto de squads) focada em “Fazendas do Cerrado”, cada uma com seu time multifuncional, coordenadas por um líder de tribo que garante troca de experiências entre elas. Essa escalabilidade &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;em rede&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; permite crescer mantendo times enxutos e eficientes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li dir=&quot;ltr&quot; aria-level=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; role=&quot;presentation&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Alinhamento com estratégia através de chapters:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; Os &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;chapters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; ou capítulos (grupos por competência, como todos os desenvolvedores, todos de negócios, etc.) asseguram que apesar da autonomia dos squads, haja coesão na empresa. Por exemplo, o capítulo de Ciência de Dados definirá padrões de modelagem, evitando que cada squad crie soluções desconexas. Assim obtém-se o &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;melhor dos dois mundos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;: autonomia local e alinhamento global.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/b&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="145" y="600" width="560" height="590" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="2GdyIjArwxJhsU-BfKCi-3" value="&lt;b id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-8ecc46a6-7fff-90c6-c3e0-82d4b47b4d3f&quot; style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;O Intelicampo adotará elementos de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;estrutura ágil&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;, inspirada em modelos de &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;squads&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;. Na prática, isso significa que embora existam os &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;times funcionais&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; (dados, parcerias, etc.), os colaboradores destes times se &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;organizam em pequenos grupos multidisciplinares&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; focados em objetivos específicos. Ao invés de trabalhar isoladamente em “silos” departamentais, um &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: italic; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;squad&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt; une profissionais de diferentes habilidades em torno de um mesmo projeto ou produto – por exemplo, melhorar a taxa de prenhez em uma fazenda leiteira piloto – com autonomia para tomar decisões rápidas. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Como funcionaria?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14.6667px; white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Squad da Fazenda Bela Vista&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;Nesse squad participariam um cientista de dados (para analisar os dados da Fazenda Bela Vista e ajustar modelos conforme suas peculiaridades), um engenheiro de dados (garantindo a integração e qualidade dos dados da fazenda), e um gerente de parceria (representando as necessidades do cliente e coordenando a aplicação das recomendações). Juntos, eles definem metas trimestrais para melhorar certos indicadores da Fazenda Bela Vista e trabalham de forma colaborativa para atingi-los. Esse squad teria &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;autonomia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt; para experimentar abordagens, desde que alinhado à estratégia geral da empresa. Em paralelo, cada membro ainda pertence ao seu &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;“capítulo” funcional&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt; – isto é, o cientista de dados troca conhecimento com outros cientistas de dados da empresa (compartilhando boas práticas de modelagem, por exemplo), o que assegura &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;padronização e excelência técnica&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt; em todas as frentes. Essa dualidade é característica da &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;matriz ágil&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;: pessoas alocadas em projetos, mas ligadas por disciplina a uma estrutura maior de suporte e aprendizado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 11pt; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; white-space-collapse: preserve; caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Vantagens:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;white-space-collapse: collapse;&quot; class=&quot;Apple-interchange-newline&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry x="190" y="130" width="560" height="430" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
      </root>
    </mxGraphModel>
